histCount = len(value)
	#return histCount
	i=0
	now = system.date.now()
	for point in value:
		row=point
		ts = system.date.fromMillis(point['t_stamp'])
		row['ts'] = ts
		duration = 0
		if (i+1)<histCount:
			#return [1,histCount]
			tsNext = system.date.fromMillis(value[i+1]['t_stamp'])
		else:
			tsNext = now
		duration = system.date.secondsBetween(ts, tsNext)
		row['duration'] = duration
		i+=1
	return value

packets = value['packets']
	now = value['now']
	rows = []
	i=0
	packetRecieved = len(packets)
	for packet in packets:
		row = {}
		duration = None
		nextTs = now
		if i<packetRecieved-1:
			nextTs = packets[i+1]['timestamp']
			
		ts = packet['timestamp']
		nextTs = system.date.parse(nextTs)
		#return [preTs,ts]
		ts = system.date.parse(ts)
		duration = system.date.secondsBetween(ts,nextTs)
		i +=1
		row['duration'] = duration
		for item in packet:
			row[item] = packet[item]
		if 'count' not in row:
			row['count'] = None
		rows.append(row)
	return rows
